comments: Had her for HDG once a week. She is a sweet lady but her lectures are Boring, it\'s a good thing she lets you bring laptops. Quiz every week; very easy, 2 papers; easy grader and 1 final exam, she used most of the questions from the quizzes so keep them! Overall easy A.

SOOOO BORING!!! I died during the 3 hour class...dry power point slides and horrible lectures! i have learned nothing! its easy...but if you are actually interested in the subject take another teacher

pretty good teacher. kinda boring but easy. a sweet lady. i had a 3 hour class with her so the class went by REALLY slow but it wasn\'t too bad. teaches mostly by slides and they are online so notes are optional. quizes are pretty easy...
